❌ CRITICAL: DATABASE_URL is missing!
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Your application is using an IN-MEMORY MOCK DATABASE.
This means:
  ❌ Data will NOT be saved
  ❌ All operations will appear to work but data is lost on restart
  ❌ Users will see "Failed to save" errors in production

🔧 How to fix:
  1. Set DATABASE_URL in your environment variables
  2. Format: postgresql://user:password@host:port/database
  3. For Vercel: Go to Settings → Environment Variables
  4. For local dev: Add to .env.local file

📚 See docs/ENV_VARIABLES.md for detailed instructions
